text: The Chile women's national under-18 and under-19 basketball team is a national basketball team of Chile, administered by the Federación de Basquetbol de Chile.FIBA National Federations – Chile, fiba.com, accessed 18 Aug 2016. It represents the country in international under-18 and under-19 (under age 18 and under age 19) women's basketball competitions. ==See also== *Chile women's national basketball team *Chile women's national under-17 basketball team *Chile men's national under-19 basketball team ==References== ==External links== * Archived records of Chile team participations under Category:Women's national under-19 basketball teams
title: Chile women's national under-19 basketball team
